item.value: 1. add -javaagent:/path/to/ja-netfilter.jar=jetbrains to your vmoptions (manual or auto) 2. log out of the jb account in the 'Licenses' window 3. use key on page https://jetbra.in/5d84466e31722979266057664941a71893322460 4. plugin 'mymap' has been deprecated since version 2022.1 5. don't care about the activation time, it is a fallback license and will not expire
